# Model {#sec:Model}

The state vector $X_t$ follows a Gaussian VAR(1) process:
$$
X_t = \mu + \Phi X_{t-1}+ \Sigma\varepsilon_t,
$$
with $\varepsilon_t \sim \mathcal{N}(0,Id)$, where $Id$ denotes the identity matrix.

